                <Header>Data / Statistics</Header>
                <Paragraph>The Office of Pipeline Safety makes available data on federally regulated and State regulated natural gas pipelines, hazardous liquid pipelines, and liquefied natural gas plants. The operators of these pipeline facilities report this data in accordance with PHMSA pipeline safety regulations. The PHMSA provides downloads of the raw  data, yearly summaries, multiyear trends of safety performance metrics, and  inventories tracking the removal of aging and other higher-risk infrastructure.</Paragraph>
